All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<Key,ObjectList<Value>>
public class MultiMap<Key,Value> extends BaseMap<Key,ObjectList<Value>>
A map from key to an ObjectList of values. Values can be added with add(Object, Object) and addAll(Object, Collection). A flat list of all values in the map can be retrieved with flatValues(). The ObjectList for a key can be retrieved with BaseMap.get(Object) or list(Object). If the list for the given key does not yet exist, list(Object) will create a new one.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
